T02TD1428E:196a-3: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ldan nyi shu rtsa bzhi ru //

T02TD1428E:196a-5: 'khor lo'i lha la rtag par phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196a-6: ma rungs 'dul mdzad rnam rgyal la sogs rnams //
T02TD1428E:196a-7: gdul bya'i dbang gis khro mo'i skur ston cing //
T02TD1428E:196a-8: sgo mtshams dag na ma rungs phyogs bdag 'dul //
T02TD1428E:196a-9: khra gdong la sogs sprul pa'i mkha' 'gro gnas //
T02TD1428E:196a-10: bya rog gdong can mkha' 'gro 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1428E:196a-11: zhal gyi nga ros 'brug stong bdud las rgyal //
T02TD1428E:196a-12: gar gyi sbyor ldan gcer bu phyag bzhi ma //
T02TD1428E:196a-13: nag mo 'jigs byed ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196a-14: shar gyi sgo srung yi dags gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1428E:196a-15: dpa' mo spyan gsum phyag rgya lnga yis mdzes //
T02TD1428E:196a-16: kha nas khrag 'dzag aa la la zhes sgrogs //
T02TD1428E:196a-17: yang dag las mtha'i dpa' mo khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1428E:196a-18: 'ug pa'i gdong can bgegs tshogs sreg mdzad ma //
T02TD1428E:196a-19: kha nas lce 'dril mche ba rnam par gtsigs //
T02TD1428E:196a-20: ha ha dgod cing spyan mig glog ltar 'gyu //
T02TD1428E:196a-21: dgra bgegs tshar gcod ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196a-22: byang gi sgo srung ljang dmar 'od ldan ma //
T02TD1428E:196a-23: mkha' 'gro mi srun rus pa'i rgyan dang ldan //
T02TD1428E:196a-24: sku mdog dmar ljang gri gug thong pa 'dzin //
T02TD1428E:196a-25: yang dag 'tsho ba'i dpa' mo khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1428E:196a-26: khyi yi gdong can thod pa'i rgyan ldan ma //
T02TD1428E:196a-27: sku mdog dmar mo phat kyi sgra sgrogs shing //
T02TD1428E:196a-28: spyan gsum sdang mig dus mtha'i me bzhin 'jigs //
T02TD1428E:196a-29: sgrub pa'i don mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196a-30: nub kyi sgo srung dpa' mo stobs ldan ma //
T02TD1428E:196a-31: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum 'byung po zil gyis gnon //
T02TD1428E:196a-32: mkha' 'gro mgo bo'i phreng bas do shal byas //
T02TD1428E:196a-33: yang dag rtsol ba'i ngo bo khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1428E:196a-34: phag gi gdong can gsang ba'i dbang phyug ma ;
T02TD1428E:196a-35: / bdud 'dul mkha' 'gro phyag rgya gar gyis skyod //
T02TD1428E:196a-36: rna cha mgul rgyan spyi gtsug nor bus brgyan //
T02TD1428E:196a-37: 'jigs byed khrag 'thung ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196a-38: lho yi sgo srung ser mo 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1428E:196b-0: zhal nas me 'bar bdud kyi dpung rnams sreg /da ma ru 'khrol kha tv'am @196b g-yon na bsgreng //
T02TD1428E:196b-1: yang dag dran pa'i dpa' mo khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1428E:196b-2: shar lhor dbang sgyur gshin rje brtan ma ni //
T02TD1428E:196b-3: g-yas sngo g-yon ser brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
T02TD1428E:196b-4: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-5: dbang phyug gsang ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-6: rdo rje mkha' 'gro sems can don brtson ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-7: rus pa'i ska rags khrag gi thig le can //
T02TD1428E:196b-8: dpal ldan mkha' 'gro dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
T02TD1428E:196b-9: dge chos yang dag bskyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-10: lho nub dri med gshin rje pho nya mo //
T02TD1428E:196b-11: g-yas ser g-yon dmar mkha' 'gro gzugs mdzes ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-12: ha ha'i sgra sgrogs gsed byed na thu rtsal can //
T02TD1428E:196b-13: mkha' 'gro dgos 'dod skong la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-14: thabs dang shes rab mnyam nyid rol pa'i sku //
T02TD1428E:196b-15: bde chen mnyam nyid mkha' 'gro kun gyi gtso //
T02TD1428E:196b-16: kha nas khrag 'dzag gri gug thod pa 'dzin //
T02TD1428E:196b-17: dge chos yang dag bsrungs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-18: nub byad mkha' 'gro gshin rje mche ba mo //
T02TD1428E:196b-19: g-yas dmar g-yon sngo spyan bgrad 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1428E:196b-20: gsang ba'i lha mo rdo rje'i glu len ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-21: stobs chen mkha' 'gro ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-22: rus pa'i dum bu khrag gi thig les brgyan //
T02TD1428E:196b-23: tshangs skud mgo bo'i phreng bas rab brgyan pas //
T02TD1428E:196b-24: rus pa'i ska rags sil sil sgra dang ldan //
T02TD1428E:196b-25: mi dge yang dag spong la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-26: byang shar gsang ba'i gshin rje 'joms byed ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-27: g-yas ljang g-yon sdo 'gying zhing rol pa'i sku //
T02TD1428E:196b-28: zhal gcig phyag bzhi g-yas brkyang gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1428E:196b-29: mkha' 'gro dbyings phyug ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-30: nyon mongs 'khrugs byed 'bar ba'i 'od ldan ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-31: khro gnyer mche gtsigs dgra bgegs zhal du gsol //
T02TD1428E:196b-32: bsnyen sgrub byed la gsang ba'i dngos grub ster //
T02TD1428E:196b-33: mi dge skyed mi byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:196b-34: dam tshig 'khor lo mi'am ci sogs 'dul //
T02TD1428E:196b-35: phyogs bzhi gdong can mtshams bzhi phyed gzugs ma //
T02TD1428E:196b-36: las kyi rigs mtshon sna tshogs rdo rjes mdzes //
T02TD1428E:196b-37: phrag dog can 'dul 'khor lo khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1428E:196b-38: sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan 'jig rten gsum //
T02TD1428E:196b-39: phyi nang brtan g-yo'i dngos po khyod rang bzhin //
T02TD1428E:197a-0: khyod kyi srid gsum rang bzhin lhan cig @197a * //
T02TD1428E:197a-2: / khyod 'dab phyogs bzhir yum bzhi mtshams bum thong //
T02TD1428E:197a-3: rim gsum dpa' bo dpa' mo bzhi bcu brgyad //
T02TD1428E:197a-4: sgo mtshams lha mo brgyad de drug cu gnyis //
T02TD1428E:197a-5: sgrub la brtser dgongs 'khor lo lngar gnas pa'i //
T02TD1428E:197a-6: lha tshogs la ni gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:197a-7: he ru ka dpal gsang ba'i grong khyer mchog / dkyil 'khor bde chen sdig pa rab 'joms pa'i //
T02TD1428E:197a-8: nyon mongs zhi bas pad nyi zlum por gnas //
T02TD1428E:197a-9: mi shes gcod phyir gri gug phreng bas mdzes //
T02TD1428E:197a-10: lha rnams mchod phyir yon tan kun ldan pa'i //
T02TD1428E:197a-11: bum pa sna tshogs bdud rtsis rab bkang nas ;
T02TD1428E:197a-12: /'dod yon snam bur lha mo kun ldan zhing //
T02TD1428E:197a-13: panytsa r'a ga rin chen pha gur ldan //
T02TD1428E:197a-14: dra ba dra phyed rin chen nyi zla dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-15: me tog phreng dang gser gyi dril bu dpyangs //
T02TD1428E:197a-16: brtson 'grus rlung bskyod dam pa'i chos sgra sgrogs //
T02TD1428E:197a-17: da ru ka sogs mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
T02TD1428E:197a-18: yon tan rgyas phyir gru bzhi sgo bzhis mdzes //
T02TD1428E:197a-19: rin chen rta babs chos 'khor gdugs kyis phub //
T02TD1428E:197a-20: yid 'od ri dags ba dan bcu drug ldan //
T02TD1428E:197a-21: rin chen ka ba tva ra na bzhis mdzes //
T02TD1428E:197a-22: ba so padma bkra shis bum pa dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-23: thod pa'i phreng ba rdo rje ra bas mdzes //
T02TD1428E:197a-24: legs pa'i sgo khyud dpal ldan phyogs bzhir gnas //
T02TD1428E:197a-25: mi dge rnams bsrung sna tshogs padma'i phyir //
T02TD1428E:197a-26: rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba bla re gur //
T02TD1428E:197a-27: mda' yi dra ba 'jigs pa'i me dpung 'bar //
T02TD1428E:197a-28: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po gshin rje dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-29: drag po sreg byed tsha tsha skar ltar 'phro //
T02TD1428E:197a-30: tshogs brgyad dag phyir dur khrod rab 'jigs byed //
T02TD1428E:197a-31: shi risha sogs byang chub shing brgyad la //
T02TD1428E:197a-32: khva gdong la sogs shing lha sprin dang bcas //
T02TD1428E:197a-33: klu dang gnod sbyin lha chen brgyad por ldan //
T02TD1428E:197a-34: dbang po me dang gshin rje srin po dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-35: chu bdag rlung lha nor bdag 'byung por ldan //
T02TD1428E:197a-36: sa yi lha mo nyi zla tshangs pa dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-37: drag po zhing skyong phyogs mtshams kun na gnas //
T02TD1428E:197a-38: mchod rten brag sogs chu dang me brgyad dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-39: nyi shu rtsa bzhi mkha' 'gro gnas pa'i sa //
T02TD1428E:197a-40: 'byung po 'dus pa ce spyang sgra sgrogs shing //
T02TD1428E:197a-41: sha za ro langs 'phra men ma brgyad dang //
T02TD1428E:197a-42: au ma dus mtshan dur khrod bdag mor bcas //
T02TD1428E:197b-0: rgyal chen bzhi sogs @197b 'jig rten dbang phyug ldan //
T02TD1428E:197b-1: grub chen brgyad sogs phyag rgya mchog ldan zhing //
T02TD1428E:197b-2: grub pa'i rnal 'byor spyod pa rnams mdzes pa'i //
T02TD1428E:197b-3: sgrub pa'i rten gyur bde gshegs kun gyi gnas //
T02TD1428E:197b-4: snod bcud dag la gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor mchog / yon tan kun ldan thar pa'i grong mchog la ;
T02TD1428E:197b-5: / bdag ni rab gus dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1428E:197b-6: lhan cig skyes dga' rang bzhin bde mchog ni //
T02TD1428E:197b-7: 'khor lo lnga sogs dur khrod bcas bstod pa'i //
T02TD1428E:197b-8: dge ba gang byung des ni 'gro ba ma lus pa //
T02TD1428E:197b-9: bde mchog la gnas myur du sangs rgyas nyid thob shog / dpal 'khor lo sdom pa'i bstod pa don thams cad grub pa rnam dag gtsug gi nor bu zhes bya ba rgyal po mchog gi dngos grub thob pa /
T02TD1428E:197b-10: slob dpon d'a ri ka pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1428E:197b-12: // / yul kha che'i mkhan po dharm'a badzra dang /
T02TD1428E:197b-13: bod kyi lo ts'a ba rgya brtson 'grus seng ges bsgyur ba'o //
T02TD1428E:197b-14: slad kyi rgya gar gyi mkhan po thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes pa'i pandi ta ku m'a ra badzra dang /
T02TD1428E:197b-15: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong nyi ma'i rdo rjes rgya gar shar phyogs kyi grong khyer mnga' ldan du bsgyur cing zhus te dag par byas so//
